snippet.title: Starlink: Battle for Atlas - Gamescom 2018: The Worlds of Atlas Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Discover the wonders of Atlas and explore seven massive open worlds, each with their own flora and fauna. Fight the Forgotten Legion and save Atlas when Starlink: Battle for Atlas launches October 16!
